songs.title: Huang’s World
songs.lyrics:
Y'all in the wrong world
Killa Cam
Welcome to Huang's World
World traveler
The food? (Woo)
Good and delicious
Shanghai, Moscow
Check out the pictures

LA, New York, M.I. yayo
London
The schedule's vicious
Whether sushi or pork
Ribeye, lamb or chicken
Turkey, turkey
Bacon , rice
Gyros
It's all finger-licking

Welcome to Huang's World
